	<h3>Regretit</h3>
	Delete reddit posts and comments from your account! This tool will not delete gilded items. You can set the following options:

	<ul>
		<li><strong>Hours: </strong>Do not delete comments younger than this many hours</li>
		<li><strong>Score Threshold: </strong>Deletes comments with less than this score</li>
		<li><strong>Sort:  </strong>Select sorting by either new, top, controversial, or hot</li>
		<li><strong>Items:  </strong>Delete items from comments, submitted, or overview</li>
		<li><strong>Trial Run:</strong> This allows you to run the script without actually deleting anything. You can see what would have been deleted! Set this to false to actually delete comments!</li>
	</ul>
